OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy with blustery showers
OL,6,Fthrough Thursday, showers heavy and
OL,7,Fperhaps thundery at times. Some
OL,8,Fbrighter spells into the afternoon and
OL,9,Ftemperatures near average for the time
OL,10,Fof year.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBecoming drier into the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight as showers
OL,14,Fincreasingly fade. Winds slowly easing
OL,15,Fto give a cooler night with some clear
OL,16,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
