OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA drier day expected Friday
OL,6,Falthough the odd shower remains
OL,7,Fpossible. Lighter winds and some good
OL,8,Fbrightness likely. Temperatures
OL,9,Fremaining near average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FRemaining unsettled and often breezy
OL,13,Fthrough the weekend and into early
OL,14,Fnext week. Outbreaks of rain or
OL,15,Fshowers interspersed with drier and
OL,16,Fbrighter interludes. Temperatures near
OL,17,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
